ml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"SEO Basics\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"page builder integrations\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=359270\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:547:\"<p>Looking to skyrocket your SEO on a website crafted with SiteOrigin Page Builder? SiteOrigin, boasting over a million active users, is a popular WordPress page builder renowned for its user-friendly approach. Its drag-and-drop interface empowers anyone, regardless of coding knowledge,&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-optimize-site-built-using-siteorigin-page-builder/\">How to Optimize a Site Built Using SiteOrigin Page Builder [Using the AIOSEO Integration]</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16236:\"<p>Looking to skyrocket your SEO on a website crafted with SiteOrigin Page Builder?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>SiteOrigin, boasting over a million active users, is a popular WordPress page builder renowned for its user-friendly approach. Its drag-and-drop interface empowers anyone, regardless of coding knowledge, to design beautiful websites.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you how to optimize a site built with the SiteOrigin page builder. The best part? Most tasks can be done directly within the page builder itself!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-siteorigin-page-builder\">What is SiteOrigin Page Builder?</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-key-features-of-siteorigin-page-builder\">Key Features of SiteOrigin Page Builder</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-is-siteorigin-page-builder-good-for-seo\">Is SiteOrigin Page Builder Good for SEO?</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-optimizing-your-siteorigin-site-with-aioseo\">Optimizing Your SiteOrigin Site with AIOSEO</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-1-install-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">Step 1: Install All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-2-access-aioseo-within-the-siteorigin-page-builder\">Step 2: Access AIOSEO within the SiteOrigin Page Builder</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-which-seo-modules-can-be-accessed-in-the-aioseo-siteorigin-integration\">Which SEO Modules Can Be Accessed in the AIOSEO/SiteOrigin Integration?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-seo-for-siteorigin-your-faqs-answered\">SEO for SiteOrigin: Your FAQs Answered</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-is-siteorigin-good-for-seo\">Is SiteOrigin good for SEO?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-is-it-necessary-to-use-an-seo-plugin-with-siteorigin\">Is it necessary to use an SEO plugin with SiteOrigin?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-the-benefits-of-using-aioseo-with-siteorigin\">What are the benefits of using AIOSEO with SiteOrigin?</a></li></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-siteorigin-page-builder\">What is SiteOrigin Page Builder?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"SiteOrigin\">SiteOrigin</a> is a robust WordPress plugin that allows users to create and design custom website layouts.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"902\" height=\"518\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/site-origin-homepage.png\" alt=\"SiteOrigin home page.\" class=\"wp-image-359866\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/site-origin-homepage.png 902w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/site-origin-homepage-300x172.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/site-origin-homepage-768x441.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/site-origin-homepage-600x345.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>SiteOrigin is renowned for its live editor that offers a true WYSIWYG (What You See Is What You Get) experience. It also has a powerful backend editor for tech-savvy users, making it perfect for web design beginners and pros.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-key-features-of-siteorigin-page-builder\">Key Features of SiteOrigin Page Builder</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Intuitive drag-and-drop interface:</strong> Effortlessly add and arrange elements to craft your desired layout.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Rows and widgets:</strong> Build intricate layouts with a flexible rows and widgets system.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Pre-designed layouts:</strong> Jumpstart your design process with a library of pre-made layouts.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-is-siteorigin-page-builder-good-for-seo\">Is SiteOrigin Page Builder Good for SEO?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>While SiteOrigin prioritizes ease of use and speed (both SEO-friendly factors), it doesn&#8217;t directly influence SEO. SEO is primarily impacted by your content, website structure, and adherence to SEO best practices.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, SiteOrigin offers features that indirectly support your SEO efforts:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fast Loading Pages:</strong> <strong>Lightweight and fast-Loading:</strong> SiteOrigin prioritizes speed and contributes to a positive user experience (UX). Both are crucial <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/google-ranking-factors/\" title=\"10 Google Ranking Factors to Act on in 2024\">ranking factors</a>.&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Responsive design:</strong> All SiteOrigin-built sites are mobile-friendly, essential for SEO in today&#8217;s <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/mobile-seo-vs-desktop-seo/\" title=\"Mobile SEO vs. Desktop SEO: A Practical WordPress Guide\">mobile-first world</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Clean code:</strong> SiteOrigin generates clean, well-structured code that search engines can easily crawl and understand. This also contributes to fast performance.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Whether you’re a pro or a newbie, if you ever need an SEO-friendly page builder, SiteOrigin should definitely be high on your list. Otherwise, consider one from our list of the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-page-builders/\" title=\"8 Best and Popular WordPress Page Builders Compared\">best page builders for WordPress</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-optimizing-your-siteorigin-site-with-aioseo\">Optimizing Your SiteOrigin Site with AIOSEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To supercharge your SEO efforts, consider integrating SiteOrigin with a dedicated SEO plugin, and that&#8217;s where <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"All in One SEO - WordPress SEO Plugin and Toolkit\" rel=\"noopener\">All in One SEO</a> (AIOSEO) comes in.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s how to elevate your SiteOrigin-built site with AIOSEO:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-1-install-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">Step 1: Install All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The first step to boosting your SEO if you use Thrive Architect is to download and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">install All In One SEO</a> AIOSEO.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO is a powerful tool that can help you boost your SiteOrigin page builder SEO.\" class=\"wp-image-151544\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-600x267.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"All in One SEO - WordPress SEO Plugin and Toolkit\" rel=\"noopener\">AIOSEO</a> is a powerful yet user-friendly SEO plugin trusted by over 3 million active marketers, bloggers, and eCommerce store brands to drive qualified traffic to their websites. The plugin offers a comprehensive suite of features and modules designed to optimize your SEO configuration. Here are some highlights:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/robots-editor/\" title=\"Robots.txt Editor\">Advanced Robots.txt Generator</a></strong>: Easily generate and customize your robots.txt file for better crawling and indexing.&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/local-seo/\" title=\"Local SEO\">Local SEO</a></strong>: Properly configure your local SEO settings to get your brand in front of the people who matter.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-the-seo-preview-tool/\" title=\"What is the SEO Preview Tool (And How to Use it to Drive More Traffic)?\">SEO Preview</a></strong>: This gives you an overview of your search and social snippets and general SEO so you can improve your optimization.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\" title=\"Features\">And more</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, if you run an online store, both AIOSEO and SiteOrigin offer powerful WooCommerce integrations. In AIOSEO&#8217;s case, this includes a specialized <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/woocommerce-seo/\" title=\"WooCommerce SEO\">WooCommerce SEO module</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-2-access-aioseo-within-the-siteorigin-page-builder\">Step 2: Access AIOSEO within the SiteOrigin Page Builder</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once installed, you&#8217;ll be able to access AIOSEO directly within the SiteOrigin editor. Just look for the AIOSEO icon in the SiteOrigin interface.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"361\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-button-in-site-origin-1024x361.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO in the SiteOrigin page builder.\" class=\"wp-image-352858\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-button-in-site-origin-1024x361.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-button-in-site-origin-300x106.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-button-in-site-origin-768x271.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-button-in-site-origin-600x212.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/aioseo-button-in-site-origin.png 1202w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Clicking this icon will open the AIOSEO settings panel, allowing you to:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Set your target focus keyword</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Craft compelling titles and meta descriptions</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Analyze your content for SEO best practices</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Implement schema markup</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Preview how your page will appear in search results</li>\n\n\n\n<li>And more!</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The beauty of this integration is the ability to optimize your on-page SEO in real time as you build your pages.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s it!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your SiteOrigin-built site is now optimized using the AIOSEO integration.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And just so you know, we also have integrations with other page builders as well, including:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/seedprod-and-aioseo-integration/\" title=\"SeedProd and AIOSEO Integration\">SeedProd</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/divi-and-aioseo-integration/\" title=\"Divi and AIOSEO Integration\">Divi</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/elementor-and-aioseo-integration/\" title=\"Elementor and AIOSEO Integration\">Elementor</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/wpbakery-and-aioseo-integration/\" title=\"WPBakery and AIOSEO Integration\">WPBakery</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/avada-and-aioseo-integration/\" title=\"Avada and AIOSEO Integration\">Avada</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Our ultimate goal is for AIOSEO to integrate seamlessly with all your favorite page builders.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-which-seo-modules-can-be-accessed-in-the-aioseo-siteorigin-integration\">Which SEO Modules Can Be Accessed in the AIOSEO/SiteOrigin Integration?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In case you’re wondering, let’s briefly look at the main SEO modules you can access in the AIOSEO/SiteOrigin integration:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>General SEO settings</strong>: Configure core SEO elements like titles, meta descriptions, and readability. This menu also has the Cornerstone Content modules, among others.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/truseo-score-analysis/\" title=\"TruSEO On-Page Analysis\">TrueSEO Highlighter</a></strong>: Makes it easy to spot on-page SEO issues and gives recommendations for fixing them.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/social-media-integration/\" title=\"Social Media Integration\">Social media settings</a></strong>: Optimize how your content appears when shared on social media platforms. This helps boost engagement and shares.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-aioseo-4-2-5-next-gen-schema-generator-to-improve-your-seo-rankings/\" title=\"Announcing AIOSEO 4.2.5: Next-Gen Schema Generator to Improve Your SEO Rankings\">Next-gen Schema generator</a></strong>: This no-code schema generator enables users to generate and output any schema markup on your site.&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/redirection-manager/\" title=\"Redirection Manager\">Redirection Manager</a></strong>: Helps you manage redirects and eliminate 404 errors, making it easier for search engines to crawl and index your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-revisions/\" title=\"SEO Revisions\">SEO Revisions</a>:</strong> Track any changes you make to your site and see their impact on your SEO. Plus, you get to see on a timeline how Google updates affect your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Advanced SEO settings</strong>: This includes robots.txt and canonical URL settings.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Having all these SEO features at your fingertips is a fantastic way to speed up the execution of your SEO tasks. As a result, your pages can be SEO-friendly by the time you finish building them.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-seo-for-siteorigin-your-faqs-answered\">SEO for SiteOrigin: Your FAQs Answered</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-is-siteorigin-good-for-seo\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Is SiteOrigin good for SEO?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>SiteOrigin is SEO-friendly because it creates fast-loading, mobile-responsive websites with clean code. However, SEO is more about your content strategy and the dedicated SEO plugin that powers it.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-is-it-necessary-to-use-an-seo-plugin-with-siteorigin\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Is it necessary to use an SEO plugin with SiteOrigin?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Having an SEO plugin like AIOSEO alongside Thrive Architect can significantly boost your SEO efforts. Having AIOSEO integrated into the page builder is even better, as the integration allows you to handle many SEO tasks on the go.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-are-the-benefits-of-using-aioseo-with-siteorigin\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What are the benefits of using AIOSEO with SiteOrigin?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Using AIOSEO inside the SiteOrigin page builder has many benefits, including:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Optimize your content for search engines directly within the SiteOrigin editor.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Get real-time SEO suggestions and scores.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Generate schema markup to provide richer information to search engines.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Manage redirects without leaving the page.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>And more.</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post has helped you learn how to use the AIOSEO/SiteOrigin integration to boost your SEO. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/wordpress-seo-tips/\" title=\"21+ WordPress SEO Tips for Beginners [Ultimate Cheat List]\">WordPress SEO cheat sheet for beginners</a> and our list of the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-woocommerce-plugins/\" title=\"20 Best WooCommerce Plugins for Your Store [2024 Edition]\">best WooCommerce plugins</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (Twitter)</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-optimize-site-built-using-siteorigin-page-builder/\">How to Optimize a Site Built Using SiteOrigin Page Builder [Using the AIOSEO Integration]</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-optimize-site-built-using-siteorigin-page-builder/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"How to Add Google Search Console to Your WordPress Website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:180:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-google-search-console-to-your-wordpress-website/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-to-add-google-search-console-to-your-wordpress-website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-